    <section id="section3">
        <h1>SgSDK初始化</h1>
        <h3>1.SgSDK 回調監聽</h3>
        <span class="badge badge-ttl">函式</span>
        <p><code>SetListener(listener: @escaping (SgSDKResult) -> Void)</code></p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">説明</span>
        <p>SgSDK 所有非同步的函式，都透過回調監聽來得到結果。</p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">範例</span>
        <p>
        <pre>SgSDK.Instance.SetListener(listener: MsgListen)</pre>
        <% include ../code/swift-setListen.html %>
        </p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">參數</span>
        <ul>
            <li>
                listener 是有一個 SgSDKResult 當參數的 delegate。
            </li>
            <li>SgSDKResult 結構</li>
            <table class="table table-striped">
                <col width="10%">
                <col width="5%">
                <col width="85%">
                <tr>
                    <th>參數名稱</th>
                    <th>型態</th>
                    <th>描述</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Code</td>
                    <td>Int</td>
                    <td><a href="/webapi-init#section5">狀態代碼</a></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Msg</td>
                    <td>String</td>
                    <td><a href="/webapi-init#section5">狀態描述</a></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Data</td>
                    <td>Any?</td>
                    <td>沒有其他資訊的話會是 nil，有資訊的話可以轉換為任一結構。</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </ul>
        <span class="badge badge-ttl">回傳</span>
        <p>無。</p>

        <h3>2.SgSDK 初始化</h3>
        <span class="badge badge-ttl">函式</span>
        <p><code>Init(GameKey: String, AppSecret: String)</code></p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">説明</span>
        <p>初始化 SgSDK 才能使用之後的所有功能。</p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">範例</span>
        <p>
        <pre>SgSDK.Instance.Init(GameKey: "YourGameKey", AppSecret: "YourAppSecret")</pre>
        </p>

        <span class="badge badge-ttl">參數</span>
        <ul>
            <li>GameKey</li>
            <li>AppSecret</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="badge badge-ttl">回傳</span>
        <p><a href="/webapi-init#section5">查看回傳值定義</a>。</p>
    </section>

    <section id="section4">
